Audio-TagLib-Shell version 1.41
===============================

A mini shell of Audio::TagLib for offering the possibility to view and
edit some basic meta data on the fly.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Audio::TagLib
  Cwd

